           SHORT="KDE 3 Mail Moniter."
cat << EOF
KBiff is a KDE "biff" or new mail notification utility. It is highly
configurable but very easy to use and setup. It supports session
managment (it "remembers" the last state it was in before you logged
off) and can be docked into the panel. It has support for mbox
(Unix-style), maildir (qmail-style), mh, POP3, IMAP4, and NNTP
mailboxes.
EOF
